- replace_component: Replace a component with a new unit.  params: {'replacement_part_id': 'str — identifier of the replacement part', 'replacement_cost': 'float (default 1.0)'}
- adjust_potentiometer: Adjust the wiper position of a potentiometer.  params: {'new_position': 'float in [0.0, 1.0]'}
- disconnect_cable: Detach a cable's connector from the circuit.  params: {'port_names': "list[str] — port names to disconnect, e.g. ['n']; null = all ports"}
- reconnect_cable: Reconnect a detached cable to its original position (or to specified nodes).  params: {'connections': 'dict[str, str] — optional: maps port_name to node_id; omit to restore original wiring'}

